  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 8th level, as a standard action, you can ask one question of a dead creature as if using @Compendium[pf1.spells.byn5q46du0ck592a]{Speak with Dead}. The dead creature you are questioning does not gain a Will saving throw if your alignments are different. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to your cleric level.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Ward Against Death power of the Repose Domain.</p>"
